text: Cossington is the name of: ;In Australia * Cossington (Turramurra), a heritage-listed house in the Sydney suburb of Turramurra ;In England * Cossington, Kent, a small settlement in Kent, home of a possible megalithic site * Cossington, Leicestershire, a village in the Soar Valley in Leicestershire * Cossington, Somerset, a village on the Polden Hills between Bridgwater and Street in Somerset
